    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available now is a driver-focused FD3S RX-7 powered by the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This unit features a robust vacuum line overhaul and verified compression across both rotors, ensuring linear power delivery through the 5-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original double-wishbone architecture and a Torsen limited-slip differential for exceptional corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes an upgraded aluminum radiator and a high-flow downpipe to mitigate rotary heat soak. A mechanically sound example perfectly dialed for spirited driving.",
