      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S is a refined blend of performance and utility, finished in a sophisticated Volcano Grey Metallic. The exterior retains a deep luster, though a few minor stone chips on the hood reflect its honest road history. Inside, the black leather interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, this vehicle is solid; it has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent major service including new brake rotors and a fresh set of all-season tires. Every electronic feature functions as intended, and the engine pulls smoothly with the signature Porsche soundtrack. It is a reliable, turn-key luxury SUV that has been cared for by a detail-oriented owner.",
